item.enchancement_unbound.orbital_strike: A strange device from a lost world, floating in the cosmos. It seems to use the firepower that comes from this world. The text on the screen reads in the Standard Galactic Alphabet, although its meaning is unclear. Something about traveling through wormholes?
item.enchancement_unbound.amethyst_shard: This item eats amethyst shards for breakfast.
item.enchancement_unbound.ice_shard_mini: This item eats packed ice and blue ice for breakfast.
death.attack.enchancement_unbound.midas_: %1$s decided to play with powers they did not deserve
death.attack.enchancement_unbound.forced: %1$s forcibly extracted experience from another and paid the price
item.enchancement_unbound.slingshot.intr: This ancient weapon used to have a name, but it was lost to the sands of time. You found it, resting near a tree that enamated unusual energy. It looks like it may have come from another dimension,
item.enchancement_unbound.slingshot.ayly: one of otherwordly creatures and towering forests...
enchantment.enchancement_unbound.curtain: Puts entities into a "curtain" state, where they take more damage depending on how many times they have been hit by this enchantment. Effect ends after one minute a while of no hits, after which the entity will become immune to being "curtained" for a few seconds.
enchantment.enchancement_unbound.ascensi: Using the shovel on the bottom of a block will make the user ascend until they reach non-solid blocks.
enchantment.enchancement_unbound.executi: About 2.5% chance to instantly execute the entity. Entities that cannot be executed, such as bosses and players, will take increased damage instead. Only activates when the target has 40% health or lower, but chance of activating increases with how wounded the target is, to a maximum of 5% at around 0.2% health remaining.
enchantment.enchancement_unbound.midas_t: Turns entities into gold upon hit. The effect will reverse when the entity touches water or rain. Does not work in ultrawarm dimensions such as the Nether. Can only be applied on gold tools.
enchantment.enchancement_unbound.apple_s: Breaking leaves has a change of dropping extra apples. Also has a chance of getting golden apples. Greatly increases the hoe's mining speed when breaking leaves.
enchantment.enchancement_unbound.soul_re: Adds experience to the attacker and drains the target of experience if it has any. Forcibly extracting experiences from another living being can't have any negative consequences, right?
